nodes.text: Wixx was a Twi'lek female member of the Balmorran resistance during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and Sith Empire. During the Republic liberation of Balmorra in 3642 BBY she was commanding the Moraine Outpost in the Moraine Territory. She asked a Republic citizen to deal with the Sith Lord Tharsis as well as several other threats to the outpost.
